Description.zhCN:
生产建筑
莫比斯空中单位生产设施。

开启：
- 隐秘运载机
- 使重型武装工程车可以建造莫比斯聚变反应堆
Description.enUS:
Production Building
Moebius air unit production facility.

Enable:
- Stealth Carrier
- Use< c val="#ColorAttackInfo">Heavy Armed Engineering Vehicle can build Moebius Fusion Reactor

Tooltip.zhCN:
坚固的莫比斯主力战机。能够变形为地对地攻击机甲。可以使用强袭轰炸技能。

可以对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
The sturdy Moebius main fighter. Able to transform into a ground-to-ground attack mecha. Can use the Assault Bombing skill.

Can be empty.

Tooltip.zhCN:
莫比斯机动突袭对空战机，可在移动中攻击。可以隐形。

可以对空和对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
Moebius is a mobile assault anti-air fighter that can attack while moving. Can become invisible.

Can be used against air and ground.

Tooltip.zhCN:
莫比斯战术打击对地战机，可在移动中攻击。可以隐形。

可以对空和对地。
Tooltip.enUS:
Moebius's tactical strike against ground fighters, which can attack while moving. Can become invisible.

Can be used against air and ground.

Tooltip.zhCN:
莫比斯空中支援单位，能够隐形。可以使用部署磁轨炮塔技能。

可以对地和对空。
侦测单位
Tooltip.enUS:
Moebius air support unit, capable of turning invisible. Can use the deploy rail turret skill.

Can be used against ground and air.
Detection unit

Tooltip.zhCN:
莫比斯空中火力支援飞船。

可以对地和对空。
侦测单位
Tooltip.enUS:
Moebius aerial fire support ship.

Can be used against ground and air.
Detection unit
Sends constructed units to the designated point. Workers rallied to resources will begin gathering automatically.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отправляет созданные войска в указанную точку. Рабочие, отправленные на месторождение минералов или веспена, автоматически начнут добычу ресурсов.

Tooltip.zhCN: 将建筑变形为移动速度缓慢的空中单位以便重新部署。建筑在着陆前无法生产单位、研发升级或使用技能。
Tooltip.enUS: Transform buildings into slow-moving air units for redeployment. Buildings cannot produce units, develop upgrades, or use skills until they land.
Halts construction of this structure. The partial construction will remain.
Tooltip.ruRU: Приостановить сооружение этого строения. Впоследствии его можно будет продолжить.

Tooltip.enUS: Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отменить текущий приказ и отдать следующий.

Tooltip.enUS: Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отменить текущий приказ и отдать следующий.

Tooltip.enUS: Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отменить текущий приказ и отдать следующий.

Tooltip.enUS: Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отменить текущий приказ и отдать следующий.

Tooltip.enUS: Cancels construction of this structure, destroying the structure and giving a partial refund.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отменить сооружение этого строения, уничтожив его и получив частичную компенсацию.

Tooltip.enUS: Selects the unit constructing this structure.
Tooltip.ruRU: Выбрать рабочего, который сооружает это строение.

Tooltip.zhCN:
莫比斯空中支援运输单位，可治疗周围的友方单位。自身永久隐形，能够降落使周围的友方单位隐形。可以使用后燃推进系统。

无法攻击。
Tooltip.enUS:
Moebius is an air support transport unit that can heal nearby friendly units. It is permanently invisible and can land to make surrounding friendly units invisible. Afterburning propulsion systems can be used.

Cannot attack.

Tooltip.zhCN: 使该建筑可以解锁更多莫比斯单位，并提升50%的充能速度。
Tooltip.enUS: Allows this building to unlock more Moebius units and increase charging speed by 50%.

Tooltip.zhCN: 使该建筑可以解锁高级莫比斯单位，并提升50%的充能速度。
Tooltip.enUS: Allows this building to unlock advanced Moebius units and increase charging speed by 50%.

Tooltip.zhCN: 使该建筑可以解锁最终莫比斯单位，并提升100%的充能速度。
Tooltip.enUS: Allows this building to unlock the final Moebius unit and increase charging speed by 100%.

Name.zhCN: 折跃暗影级战列巡航舰

Tooltip.zhCN:
莫比斯先进主力战舰，能够使用多种武器攻击敌人。可以使用粒子炮和战术折跃技能。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
Moebius is an advanced main battleship that can use a variety of weapons to attack the enemy. Can use particle cannon and tactical warp skills.

Can be used against ground and air.

Name.zhCN: 折跃军团突击运载母舰

Tooltip.zhCN:
强大的莫比斯重型运输舰，可释放突击战机攻击敌方单位。几乎能够瞬间完成对舱载单位的部署。可以使用战术折跃技能。

可以对地和对空。
Tooltip.enUS:
The powerful Moebius heavy transport ship, which can release assault fighters to attack enemy units. Deployment of onboard units can be completed almost instantly. Can use tactical jump skills.

Can be used against ground and air.
